em said he's used to the conditions.\", \"from\": 4999, \"to\": 5046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5006, \"end\": 5012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 5031, \"to\": 5045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Avideoin May on Nadeem's Instagram profile showed him throwing in 45C (113F) weather.\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5064, \"end\": 5070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}, {\"begin\": 5073, \"end\": 5082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3742720148023455e-42, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Avideoin May\", \"from\": 5048, \"to\": 5060}, {\"ngram\": \"113F) weather\", \"from\": 5119, \"to\": 5132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"45\\u00b0C fuels my passion for success,\\\" he wrote.\", \"from\": 5134, \"to\": 5180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my passion\", \"from\": 5146, \"to\": 5156}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem was born on January 2, 1997, in a small village near the city of Mian Channu in southern Punjab state, about 300km (186 miles) southwest of the megacity of Lahore.\", \"from\": 5184, \"to\": 5354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5256, \"e