as famous in the village for his bowling,\\\" Shahid recalled.\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6409, \"end\": 6415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.594074870632419e-14, \"text\": \"Shahid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 6379, \"to\": 6390}, {\"ngram\": \"his bowling\", \"from\": 6395, \"to\": 6406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He could single-handedly get teams out.\", \"from\": 6426, \"to\": 6466, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 6456, \"to\": 6461}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he'd have continued to play, I am sure he could have become as fast as Shoaib Akhtar,\\\" he said, comparing Nadeem to one of Pakistan's fastest bowlers, who retired in 2011.\", \"from\": 6467, \"to\": 6641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6541, \"end\": 6554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoaib_Akhtar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shoaib Akhtar\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoaib_Akhtar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shoaib_Akhtar\"}, {\"begin\": 6593, \"end\": 6601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999996144434423, \"rank\": 3.855568012740783e-07, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 6576, \"to\": 6582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Nadeem's father and two older brothers discouraged him from pursuing cricket.\", \"from\": 6643, \"to\": 6724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6647, \"end\": 6653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\"