ell-built, started to compete in school athletics events, including sprints, long jump, triple jump, discus throwing and javelin.\", \"from\": 7042, \"to\": 7235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his brother's encouragement\", \"from\": 7050, \"to\": 7077}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 7079, \"to\": 7085}, {\"ngram\": \"school athletics events\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7162}, {\"ngram\": \"sprints\", \"from\": 7174, \"to\": 7181}, {\"ngram\": \"long jump\", \"from\": 7183, \"to\": 7192}, {\"ngram\": \"triple jump\", \"from\": 7194, \"to\": 7205}, {\"ngram\": \"discus throwing\", \"from\": 7207, \"to\": 7222}, {\"ngram\": \"javelin\", \"from\": 7227, \"to\": 7234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then in 2011, Rasheed Ahmed Saqi, a hotelier and resident of Mian Channu who scouts and invests in new athletic talent, saw Nadeem compete.\", \"from\": 7237, \"to\": 7376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7298, \"end\": 7309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8238061390691224e-29, \"text\": \"Mian Channu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rasheed Ahmed Saqi\", \"from\": 7251, \"to\": 7269}, {\"ngram\": \"resident\", \"from\": 7286, \"to\": 7294}, {\"ngram\": \"new athletic talent\", \"from\": 7336, \"to\": 7355}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 7361, \"to\": 7367}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was a member of the Punjab Athletic Federation, and there was a local competition I organised where I saw this lanky kid who made quite an impression in track and field games, especially javelin and shot put.\", \"from\": 7378, \"to\": 7589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7401, \"end\": 7407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0230747532588403e-21, \"text\": \"Punjab\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Punjab\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7393}, {\"ngram\": \"a local competition\", \"from\": 7443, \"to\": 7462}, {\"ngram\": \"this lanky kid\", \"from\": 7487, \"to\": 7501}, {\"ngram\": \"quite an impression\", \"from\": 7511, \"to\": 7530}, {\"ngram\": \"track and field games\", \"from\": 7534, \"to\": 7555}, {\"ngram\": \"especially javelin\", \"from\": 7557, \"to\": 7575}, {\"ngram\": \"shot put\", \"from\": 7580, \"to\": 7588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I noticed he was strong.\", \"from\": 7590, \"to\": 7614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He ran well.\", \"from\": 7615, \"to\": 7627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I thought, maybe if I can help train him, he could make a difference,\\\" said the 69-year-old, who had competed on the provincial level in track and field, including in javelin throw, in the 1960s and 1970s.\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 7687, \"to\": 7699}, {\"ngram\": \"the provincial level\", \"from\": 7744, \"to\": 7764}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 7768, \"to\": 7773}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 7778, \"to\": 7783}, {\"ngram\": \"javelin throw\", \"from\": 7798, \"to\": 7811}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1960s\", \"from\": 7816, \"to\": 7825}, {\"ngram\": \"1970s\", \"from\": 7830, \"to\": 7835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two weeks after the event, Saqi, was sitting in a hotel he owns in Mian Channu when Ashraf brought his son to his office.\", \"from\": 7838, \"to\": 7959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7905, \"end\": 7916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8238061390691224e-29, \"text\": \"Mian Channu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mian_Channu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 7854, \"to\": 7863}, {\"ngram\": \"Saqi\", \"from\": 7865, \"to\": 7869}, {\"ngram\": \"a hotel\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7893}, {\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 7922, \"to\": 7928}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 7937, \"to\": 7944}, {\"ngram\": \"his office\", \"from\": 7948, \"to\": 7958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Arshad is your son and your responsibility from today,\\\" Ashraf told him.\", \"from\": 7960, \"to\": 8033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arshad\", \"from\": 7961, \"to\": 7967}, {\"ngram\": \"your son\", \"from\": 7971, \"to\": 7979}, {\"ngram\": \"your responsibility\", \"from\": 7984, \"to\": 8003}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 8009, \"to\": 8014}, {\"ngram\": \"Ashraf\", \"from\": 8017, \"to\": 8023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And from that day onwards, I have taken him under my wings,\\\" said Saqi, who became Nadeem's first coach and mentor.\", \"from\": 8035, \"to\": 8151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8119, \"end\": 8125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 8045, \"to\": 8053}, {\"ngram\": \"my wings\", \"from\": 8086, \"to\": 8094}, {\"ngram\": \"Saqi\", \"from\": 8102, \"to\": 8106}, {\"ngram\": \"mentor\", \"from\": 8144, \"to\": 8150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around this time, Shahid started working as a police officer while his eldest brother joined the army.\", \"from\": 8155, \"to\": 8257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8173, \"end\": 8179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.594074870632419e-14, \"text\": \"Shahid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shahid\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this time\", \"from\": 8162, \"to\": 8171}, {\"ngram\": \"a police officer\", \"from\": 8199, \"to\": 8215}, {\"ngram\": \"his eldest brother\", \"from\": 8222, \"to\": 8240}, {\"ngram\": \"the army\", \"from\": 8248, \"to\": 8256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They urged Nadeem to pursue javelin throwing.\", \"from\": 8259, \"to\": 8304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 8270, \"to\": 8276}, {\"ngram\": \"javelin throwing\", \"from\": 8287, \"to\": 8303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He has always been a shy, quiet person who often keeps to himself.\", \"from\": 8305, \"to\": 8372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shy, quiet person\", \"from\": 8325, \"to\": 8344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We both knew that he liked the sport but never spoke about it publicly,\\\" Shadid said.\", \"from\": 8373, \"to\": 8458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 8400, \"to\": 8409}, {\"ngram\": \"Shadid\", \"from\": 8446, \"to\": 8452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We told him, 'Do not worry about money.\", \"from\": 8459, \"to\": 8499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 8493, \"to\": 8498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have jobs.\", \"from\": 8500, \"to\": 8513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 8508, \"to\": 8512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can support our home.'\\\"\", \"from\": 8514, \"to\": 8540, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our home\", \"from\": 8529, \"to\": 8537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Pakistan's sports structure revolving around public sector organisations that offer employment opportunities to talented athletes, Nadeem's athletic exploits generated attention locally, and various departments sought him out a few years later.\", \"from\": 8542, \"to\": 8791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8547, \"end\": 8555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999996144434