on\", \"from\": 11059, \"to\": 11094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sporting event, which took place in Guwahati, India, was also the first time Nadeem competed against the then-emerging Indian star Neeraj Chopra.\", \"from\": 11097, \"to\": 11246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11137, \"end\": 11145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guwahati\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.579269501162948e-22, \"text\": \"Guwahati\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guwahati\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guwahati\"}, {\"begin\": 11147, \"end\": 11152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999447545649, \"rank\": 5.5245196101758745e-08, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11220, \"end\": 11226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999914916771, \"rank\": 7.937450853421812e-09, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 11232, \"end\": 11245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neeraj Chopra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neeraj_Chopra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sporting event\", \"from\": 11097, \"to\": 11115}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 11128, \"to\": 11133}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 11163, \"to\": 11177}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 11178, \"to\": 11184}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem, who went into the tournament with a niggle in his throwing elbow, still managed a throw of 78.33 metres (257ft), winning his first international medal, a bronze, with Chopra securing gold.\", \"from\": 11248, \"to\": 11444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 11248, \"to\": 11254}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 11270, \"to\": 11284}, {\"ngram\": \"a niggle\", \"from\": 11290, \"to\": 11298}, {\"ngram\": \"his throwing elbow\", \"from\": 11302, \"to\": 11320}, {\"ngram\": \"a throw\", \"from\": 11336, \"to\": 11343}, {\"ngram\": \"78.33 metres\", \"from\": 11347, \"to\": 11359}, {\"ngram\": \"his first international medal\", \"from\": 11377, \"to\": 11406}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 11408, \"to\": 11416}, {\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 11423, \"to\": 11429}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 11439, \"to\": 11443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The previous Pakistani record lasted for nearly two decades, so I was very pleased with my effort,\\\" Nadeem reflected.\", \"from\": 11446, \"to\": 11564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11460, \"end\": 11469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999305966159251, \"rank\": 6.537216317233928e-05, \"text\": \"Pakistani\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly two decades\", \"from\": 11488, \"to\": 11506}, {\"ngram\": \"my effort\", \"from\": 11535, \"to\": 11544}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 11547, \"to\": 11553}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spears were once hurled as weapons for hunting and fighting.\", \"from\": 11568, \"to\": 11628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spears\", \"from\": 11568, \"to\": 11574}, {\"ngram\": \"weapons\", \"from\": 11595, \"to\": 11602}, {\"ngram\": \"hunting\", \"from\": 11607, \"to\": 11614}, {\"ngram\": \"fighting\", \"from\": 11619, \"to\": 11627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a sport, it was one of the original disciplines at the ancient Olympic Games in Greece.\", \"from\": 11629, \"to\": 11719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11712, \"end\": 11718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9849345324759182, \"rank\": 0.015295849467166748, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 11632, \"to\": 11639}, {\"ngram\": \"the original disciplines\", \"from\": 11655, \"to\": 11679}, {\"ngram\": \"the ancient Olympic Games\", \"from\": 11683, \"to\": 11708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In its modern iteration, the sport has been part of the games since the 1908 London Olympics.\", \"from\": 11721, \"to\": 11814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its modern iteration\", \"from\": 11724, \"to\": 11744}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 11746, \"to\": 11755}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 11765, \"to\": 11769}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 11773, \"to\": 11782}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1908 London Olympics\", \"from\": 11789, \"to\": 11813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the decades, the spear has gone through various changes.\", \"from\": 11816, \"to\": 11877, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decades\", \"from\": 11821, \"to\": 11832}, {\"ngram\": \"the spear\", \"from\": 11834, \"to\": 11843}, {\"ngram\": \"various changes\", \"from\": 11861, \"to\": 11876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important change to the javelin, however, was made in 1986 after the feats of East German athlete Uwe Hohn, who in 1984 threw the spear an astonishing distance of 104.8m [343.8ft], raising safety concerns.\", \"from\": 11879, \"to\": 12093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11966, \"end\": 11977, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9999998375260607, \"rank\": 1.6247430720856027e-07, \"text\": \"East German\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 11986, \"end\": 11994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uwe_Hohn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Uwe Hohn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uwe_Hohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uwe_Hohn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most important change\", \"from\": 11879, \"to\": 11904}, {\"ngram\": \"the javelin\", \"from\": 11908, \"to\": 11919}, {\"ngram\": \"the feats\", \"from\": 11953, \"to\": 11962}, {\"ngram\": \"the spear\", \"from\": 12014, \"to\": 12023}, {\"ngram\": \"an astonishing distance\", \"from\": 12024, \"to\": 12047}, {\"ngram\": \"safety concerns\", \"from\": 12077, \"to\": 12092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The javelin at that time would also fall flat instead of on its tip, often resulting in arguments over the validity of the throw.\", \"from\": 12094, \"to\": 12223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The javelin\", \"from\": 12094, \"to\": 12105}, {\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 12109, \"to\": 12118}, {\"ngram\": \"its tip\", \"from\": 12154, \"to\": 12161}, {\"ngram\": \"arguments\", \"from\": 12182, \"to\": 12191}, {\"ngram\": \"the validity\", \"from\": 12197, \"to\": 12209}, {\"ngram\": \"the throw\", \"from\": 12213, \"to\": 12222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Consequently, the spear wasredesignedto bring the centre of gravity 3cm (1.2 inches) forward, ensuring the javelin landed tip first and also reducing the flight range.\", \"from\": 12225, \"to\": 12392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spear wasredesignedto\", \"from\": 12239, \"to\": 12264}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 12271, \"to\": 12281}, {\"ngram\": \"gravity\", \"from\": 12285, \"to\": 12292}, {\"ngram\": \"3cm\", \"from\": 12293, \"to\": 12296}, {\"ngram\": \"1.2 inches\", \"from\": 12298, \"to\": 12308}, {\"ngram\": \"the javelin\", \"from\": 12328, \"to\": 12339}, {\"ngram\": \"tip\", \"from\": 12347, \"to\": 12350}, {\"ngram\": \"the flight range\", \"from\": 12375, \"to\": 12391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 24 male athletes have thrown beyond the 90-metre mark, some multiple times.\", \"from\": 12394, \"to\": 12474, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only 24 male athletes\", \"from\": 12394, \"to\": 12415}, {\"ngram\": \"the 90-metre mark\", \"from\": 12435, \"to\": 12452}, {\"ngram\": \"some multiple times\", \"from\": 12454, \"to\": 12473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Czech athlete Jan Zelezny, considered the greatest javelin athlete of all time, retains the world record with a throw of 98.48 metres (323ft) in 1996 using the redesigned spear.\", \"from\": 12475, \"to\": 12652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12475, \"end\": 12480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"score\": 0.7466534668027734, \"rank\": 0.33324483260188453, \"text\": \"Czech\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 12489, \"end\": 12500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_\\u017delezn\\u00fd\", \"score\": 0.9999990025758478, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jan Zelezny\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_\\u017delezn\\u00fd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_\\u017delezn\\u00fd\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the greatest javelin athlete\", \"from\": 12513, \"to\": 12541}, {\"ngram\": \"all time\", \"from\": 12545, \"to\": 12553}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 12563, \"to\": 12579}, {\"ngram\": \"a throw\", \"from\": 12585, \"to\": 12592}, {\"ngram\": \"98.48 metres\", \"from\": 12596, \"to\": 12608}, {\"ngram\": \"the redesigned spear\", \"from\": 12631, \"to\": 12651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zelezny went on to launch more than 30 throws that crossed the 90-metre mark.\", \