all changes\", \"from\": 13171, \"to\": 13184}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 13189, \"to\": 13193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On July 7, Nadeem participated in the Diamond League competition in Paris, his first international event since his surgery in February.\", \"from\": 13242, \"to\": 13377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13280, \"end\": 13294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.136832885881101e-15, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\"}, {\"begin\": 13310, \"end\": 13315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5620823909469703e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 13245, \"to\": 13249}, {\"ngram\": \"Nadeem\", \"from\": 13253, \"to\": 13259}, {\"ngram\": \"his first international event\", \"from\": 13317, \"to\": 13346}, {\"ngram\": \"his surgery\", \"from\": 13353, \"to\": 13364}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 13368, \"to\": 13376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wearing a white vest emblazoned with \\\"Nadeem\\\", the Pakistani athlete managed a best throw of 84.21 metres (276ft) on his fifth attempt, which landed him in fourth position.\", \"from\": 13379, \"to\": 13551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13430, \"end\": 13439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999305966159251, \"rank\": 6.537216317233928e-05, \"text\": \"Pakistani\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a white vest\", \"from\": 13387, \"to\": 13399}, {\"ngram\": \"a best throw\", \"from\": 13456, \"to\": 13468}, {\"ngram\": \"84.21 metres\", \"from\": 13472, \"to\": 13484}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth attempt\", \"from\": 13496, \"to\": 13513}, {\"ngram\": \"fourth position\", \"from\": 13535, \"to\": 13550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grimacing after every throw, it was evident that Nadeem was easing his way into a rhythm, something his coach confirmed later.\", \"from\": 13553, \"to\": 13679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13602, \"end\": 13608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every throw\", \"from\": 13569, \"to\": 13580}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 13620, \"to\": 13627}, {\"ngram\": \"a rhythm\", \"from\": 13633, \"to\": 13641}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 13653, \"to\": 13662}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The first and foremost aim was to see how well the rehabilitation has been, and now we can work on making small tweaks in training and just fine-tuning,\\\" Butt said.\", \"from\": 13681, \"to\": 13846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first and foremost aim\", \"from\": 13682, \"to\": 13708}, {\"ngram\": \"the rehabilitation\", \"from\": 13729, \"to\": 13747}, {\"ngram\": \"small tweaks\", \"from\": 13788, \"to\": 13800}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 13804, \"to\": 13812}, {\"ngram\": \"just fine-tuning\", \"from\": 13817, \"to\": 13833}, {\"ngram\": \"Butt\", \"from\": 13836, \"to\": 13840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nadeem credits his coach with helping his quick recovery.\", \"from\": 13848, \"to\": 13905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 13863, \"to\": 13872}, {\"ngram\": \"his quick recovery\", \"from\": 13886, \"to\": 13904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the world of elite athletics, it all comes down to your supp