m\": 14848, \"to\": 14859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, it is at the discretion of the home country or sports authorities to give such prizes.\", \"from\": 14861, \"to\": 14956, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the discretion\", \"from\": 14879, \"to\": 14893}, {\"ngram\": \"the home country\", \"from\": 14897, \"to\": 14913}, {\"ngram\": \"sports authorities\", \"from\": 14917, \"to\": 14935}, {\"ngram\": \"such prizes\", \"from\": 14944, \"to\": 14955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, from the 2024 Olympics, gold medal winners will receive a $50,000 reward, and from the Los Angeles Olympics in 2028, prize money will also be awarded to silver and bronze medal winners.\", \"from\": 14958, \"to\": 15152, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15054, \"end\": 15074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999854481, \"rank\": 1.4966171622254462e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 14972, \"to\": 14989}, {\"ngram\": \"gold medal winners\", \"from\": 14991, \"to\": 15009}, {\"ngram\": \"a $50,000 reward\", \"from\": 15023, \"to\": 15039}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 15084, \"to\": 15095}, {\"ngram\": \"silver and bronze medal winners\", \"from\": 15120, \"to\": 15151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While training, Nadeem spends time away from his wife, two sons and a daughter, who live in Mian Channu, and stays in the Punjab sports board's hostel for athletes.\", \"from\": 15154, \"to\": 15318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15170, \"end\": 15176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.9934085430122968, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadeem_Baig_(actor)\", \"dbpedi