\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 17025, \"to\": 17036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Look, India is our neighbour.\", \"from\": 17048, \"to\": 17078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17055, \"end\": 17060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999447545649, \"rank\": 5.5245196101758745e-08, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our neighbour\", \"from\": 17064, \"to\": 17077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People on both sides say a lot of things about each other's country, but this is what sports teaches us - to be friendly and that we do not have to focus on our differences.\\\"\", \"from\": 17079, \"to\": 17253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 17079, \"to\": 17085}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 17089, \"to\": 17099}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 17104, \"to\": 17109}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 17113, \"to\": 17119}, {\"ngram\": \"each other's country\", \"from\": 17126, \"to\": 17146}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 17165, \"to\": 17171}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 17180, \"to\": 17182}, {\"ngram\": \"our differences\", \"from\": 17236, \"to\": 17251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"I know I have great rivals like Chopra or Peters or others, but ultimately, I compete against myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 17255, \"to\": 17372, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"great rivals\", \"from\": 17284, \"to\": 17296}, {\"ngram\": \"Chopra\", \"from\": 17302, \"to\": 17308}, {\"ngram\": \"Peters\", \"from\": 17312, \"to\": 17318}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 17322, \"to\": 17328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 17374, \"to\": 17400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English\", \"from\